	<string>This app uses your location to provide streaming content relevant to your area.</string>
	<key>NSLocationAlwaysAndWhenInUseUsageDescription</key>
	<string>This app uses your location to offer better streaming suggestions based on your location, even when running in the background.</string>
	<key>NSMicrophoneUsageDescription</key>
	<string>his app uses the microphone for audio streaming and voice interactions.</string>
